snippet.textDisplay: It takes a true knowledge and mastery of music generally - and Qawwali specifically - to be able to properly appreciate this brilliant take on the original track from Al Hilaal.  I was doubtful upon reading the description in the 'about' section above, but I gave it a chance and am SO glad that I did.  It's tastefully done (unlike most modern remakes of anything!) and these gentlemen really sing well.  So for all of you haters out there, please try understanding the intention behind this remake before judging it so negatively.  And you ought to consider refraining from the use of rude and insulting language in your comments because that is in direct contravention to the spirit of this song - regardless of who sings it and when.
